{
  "texts": [
    "Additionally, population construction and evaluation can be improved across modalities.",
    "Furthermore, as LLMs technologies continue to progress, evolutionary operators based on LLMs will also benefit and improve the performance of EAs.",
    "With increasing model scales and stronger generalization capabilities, evolutionary operators based on LLMs will be better able to simulate more complex evolutionary mechanisms precisely.",
    "This provides potential for tackling problems in complex search spaces.",
    "The emerging and rapidly advancing field of LLMs will also provide more choices for EAs."
  ]
}